special_powers.name: VOICES IN MY HEAD
special_powers.description: Agent X can't be the target of Mind Control.

special_powers.name: I GOT LIKE, HALF OF DEADPOOL'S HEALING FACTOR, TOPS
special_powers.description: Agent X can use Regeneration.  If he has no action tokens, he can use it as a free action.

special_powers.name: MERC WITH A MOUTH
special_powers.description: Give Headpool a free action and attach a Word Balloon to him, replacing any currently attached. Headpool can use the associated effects.

special_powers.name: ZOMBIE VIRUS THAT DESTROYED A UNIVERSE
special_powers.description: When Headpool damages a character that doesn't have the Z-Virus keyword, give that character a Virus token if it has less than 5 Virus tokens. Give Headpool a free action and choose a character with a Virus token; modify its speed and range values -1 for each Virus token on it until your next turn.

special_powers.name: HAIL MARY, BOSS!
special_powers.description: Adjacent friendly characters can use Telekinesis, but only to make a ranged combat attack as if Headpool were a light object. If they do, instead of being destroyed, place Headpool adjacent to the target character.

special_powers.name: IMMORTAL ZOMBIE HEAD THAT EVERYONE WANTS
special_powers.description: Headpool ignores other characters' Poison and all but 1 damage that would be dealt to him. This power can't be countered or ignored.

special_powers.name: MERC WITH A MOUTH
special_powers.description: Give Dogpool a free action and attach a Word Balloon to him, replacing any currently attached. Dogpool can use the associated effects.

special_powers.name: "BARK" WHAT'D YA FIND BOY? TIMMY IN THE WELL AGAIN?
special_powers.description: Dogpool can use Perplex, but only to decrease a defense value. When he uses Perplex, he can use Improved Targeting: Hindering and targeted characters can't use Stealth this turn.

special_powers.name: MINION: NUMERICAL ORDER
special_powers.description: Give Secret Empire Agent a power action when a friendly character with the Secret Empire keyword and "number" in their name is within 8 squares and choose Outwit, Perplex, or Probability Control. Secret Empire Agent can use the chosen power until your next turn

special_powers.name: WE MUST BE STRONG TO CHANGE THEIR IGNORANT MINDS
special_powers.description: When a friendly character named Flag-Smasher is within 8 squares, U.L.T.I.M.A.T.U.M. Soldier can use Toughness and Willpower.

special_powers.name: DESTROY ALL NATIONAL SYMBOLS!
special_powers.description: Opposing characters of 150 or less within 3 squares can't use team abilities if those squares are within line of fire.

special_powers.name: RETURN FROM DEATH
special_powers.description: When Hand Ninja would be KO'd while adjacent to a friendly character with The Hand keyword, roll a d6. On a result of 5-6, Hand Ninja isn't KO'd and after actions resolve, is placed in your starting area on click #2 instead.

special_powers.name: THERE'S ALWAYS MORE NINJAS
special_powers.description: When Hand Ninja is adjacent to at least one friendly character with the Hand keyword, Hand Ninja can make a close combat attack as a free action.

special_powers.name: CAPTURE SUBJECTS
special_powers.description: Weapon X Scientist can use Telekinesis but only to place opposing characters or characters with the Weapon X keyword.

special_powers.name: WE CAN ALWAYS FIND YOU
special_powers.description: Weapon X Scientist can use Outwit. When he does, he may target characters that can use Battle Fury or have the Weapon X keyword regardless of range or line of fire.

special_powers.name: SECRET MASTERMIND
special_powers.description: When adjacent to a friendly character, The Professor can't be targeted by opposing characters.

special_powers.name: MASTERMIND OF THE WEAPON X PROGRAM
special_powers.description: The Professor can use Empower and Outwit with a range value of 8. When he does and counters a power on a character with a range value of 0, he may immediately Mind Control as a free action targeting that character with a ranged combat attack regardless of range, and takes no damage for using this Mind Control.

special_powers.name: BIONIC ARM
special_powers.description: Misty Knight can use Close Combat Expert.

special_powers.name: HEROES FOR HIRE DISPATCHER
special_powers.description: Misty Knight can use Leadership. When she does and succeeds, friendly characters that share a keyword with her and began that action adjacent to her can use Sidestep this turn.

special_powers.name: I CAN COMMAND INSECTS WITH MY MIND! WELL, IF WE'RE ALREADY FRIENDS...
special_powers.description: Give Humbug a free action, choose an opposing character occupying hindering terrain within 6 squares, and roll a d6. On a result of 4-6, choose one: deal 1 penetrating damage to that character or counter 1 power that character possesses until your next turn.

special_powers.name: WILD PACK, ASSEMBLE!
special_powers.description: Adjacent friendly characters that share a keyword with Silver Sable can use the team ability she is copying.

special_powers.name: LEADER OF THE WILD PACK
special_powers.description: Silver Sable can use Leadership and Outwit. When she uses Leadership, for each other friendly character that can use Leadership, modify the result of her d6 roll by +1.

special_powers.name: DETACHABLE ROCKET HANDS
special_powers.description: Give Weapon X a power action when there are no Rocket Hand tokens on the map placed by him. Place up to 2 Rocket Hand bystander tokens as described on this card on the map within 5 squares and line of fire. For each of these tokens on the map, Weapon X modifies his attack values by -1.

special_powers.name: LIQUID METAL WEAPONS
special_powers.description: Weapon X can use Blades/Claws/Fangs, Energy Explosion, and Penetrating/Psychic Blast. If he uses one or more of these, at the end of the turn deal him 1 unavoidable damage if he didn't hit any opposing characters this turn.

special_powers.name: CHOKE THE LIFE OUT OF YA
special_powers.description: When a character fails to break away from Anaconda, deal them 1 penetrating damage.

special_powers.name: CONSTRICTING LIMBS
special_powers.description: Anaconda can use Plasticity. Opposing characters within 3 squares and line of fire treat Anaconda as adjacent for movement purposes.

special_powers.name: SO - SHOOT OUR WAY IN, OR SHOULD I TAKE OUT THE WALL?
special_powers.description: Hammerhead can use Charge and Running Shot.

special_powers.name: I ONLY HIRE THE VERY BEST HIT-MEN... THAT KINGPIN DOESN'T
special_powers.description: Hammerhead can use Enhancement. If an adjacent friendly character can use at least one of Precision Strike, the Sharpshooter ability, or Improved Targeting: Hindering it can use all of them.

special_powers.name: ALLY OF HEROES
special_powers.description: At the beginning of the game, choose Enhancement or Empower. Daredevil can use that power this game. A Heroes for Hire themed team may include Daredevil and is still a theme team.

special_powers.name: RADAR SENSES
special_powers.description: Daredevil can use Super Senses.

special_powers.name: ANIMUS/VAMP
special_powers.description: When Animus heals or takes damage and actions resolve, you may replace her with DP #017 Vamp on the same click number. That character can use Shape Change until your next turn, even if this ability is lost.

special_powers.name: MENTAL BRUTE
special_powers.description: Animus can use Penetrating/Psychic Blast, Super Strength, and Telekinesis.

special_powers.name: VAMP/ANIMUS
special_powers.description: When Vamp heals or takes damage and actions resolve, you may replace her with DP #016 Animus on the same click number. That character can use Shape Change until your next turn, even if this ability is lost.

special_powers.name: ABSORBO-BELT
special_powers.description: Give Vamp a free action and choose a character within 5 squares. Until your next turn, Vamp can use the standard powers that character possesses as long as they are within 5 squares.

special_powers.name: YOU HAVE TO STAY IN THE DEADHUT
special_powers.description: At the end of your turn, if Blind Al is not in a starting area, deal her 1 damage.

special_powers.name: OLD-BOOBY-TRAP
special_powers.description: Give Blind Al a power action when she occupies a starting area. Deal 1 penetrating damage to a character in that starting area and place that character adjacent to but outside of that starting area.

special_powers.name: DEADPOOL LISTENS TO ME... SOMETIMES
special_powers.description: Blind Al can use Perplex to target a character that hasn't already been targeted by Perplex this turn. She can use it to target a character in your starting area, or to target a character with "Deadpool" in its name anywhere on the map.

special_powers.name: MERC WITH A MOUTH
special_powers.description: Give Deadpool a free action and attach a Word Balloon to him, replacing any currently attached.  Deadpool can use the associated effects.

special_powers.name: I'VE BEEN KICKED OFF BETTER TEAMS THAN THIS, BUT YOU SEEM TO BE RECRUITING!
special_powers.description: During your first turn, you may choose to have Deadpool loose all keywords.  If you do, he may choose a copyable team ability an opposing character possesses, and he may use it this game.

special_powers.name: RIDICULOUS REGENERATION
special_powers.description: Whenever Deadpool would be dealt damage from an attack; roll a d6 instead.  On a result of 1, he takes that damage plus 1.  On a result of a 2-3 he takes the normal amount of damage.  On a result of 4-5 he takes 1 damage. On a result of a 6, he heals 1 damage.  This power can't be countered or ignored.

special_powers.name: AVX #T001 AVENGERS OR AVX #T002 X-MEN
special_powers.description: When this team character is attached, opposing characters can't use the Avengers or X-Men team abilities.

special_powers.name: MERC WITH A MOUTH
special_powers.description: Give Evil Deadpool a free action and attach a Word Balloon to him, replacing any currently attached. He can use the associated effects.

special_powers.name: BACKWARDS ARM - FOR BETTER SHOOTING!
special_powers.description: When Evil Deadpool makes a close combat attack, after actions resolve, he can make a ranged combat attack targeting a character within range and in a direct line of fire opposite from the close combat attack. For this attack, he can use Improved Targeting: Adjacent.

special_powers.name: WEIRD REGENERATION FROM LEFTOVER PARTS
special_powers.description: Evil Deadpool can use Regeneration.  Choose an opponent to roll another d6. If the opponent's roll is higher than your d6 roll, add the two results together and subtract 2.  Evil Deadpool is healed of damage equal to this amount instead.  Each time Evil Deadpool would heal past his starting click in this way, modify his combat values by +1 for the rest of the game, even if this power is lost.

special_powers.name: I THOUGHT I FIXED THAT!
special_powers.description: Give Weasel a free action and choose a friendly character within 4 squares and line of fire, or a friendly character with "Deadpool" in its name anywhere on the map. This turn, each time the chosen character makes an attack roll for a ranged combat attack and misses by 1, you may reroll that attack roll unless it's a critical miss.

special_powers.name: TECH-GURU TO THE UNDERWORLD
special_powers.description: Weasel can use Enhancement, and once per turn when he does, also modify the attacking character's attack and range values by +1.

special_powers.name: MERC WITH A MOUTH
special_powers.description: Give Kidpool a free action and attach a Word Balloon to him, replacing any currently attached. Kidpool can use the associated effects.

special_powers.name: NON-COPYRIGHT-INFRINGING DUAL "LIGHT SWORDS"
special_powers.description: Kidpool can use Blades/Claws/Fangs, Flurry, and Precision Strike. When he uses Flurry and hits, his second attack must target a different character.

special_powers.name: IDENTITY THAT WOULD SHOCK THE NATION
special_powers.description: Number One can use Shape Change. If he does and fails, for that attack, increase his defense value by half of the result.

special_powers.name: YOU WON'T HAVE ME TO KICK AROUND ANYMORE
special_powers.description: Give Number One a double power action. Number One can use Pulse Wave as a free action. Unless already modified by this effect, hit opposing characters modify their combat values by -1 for the rest of the game, even when this power is lost.

special_powers.name: LEADERS MUST BE CONTROVERSIAL
special_powers.description: Number One can use Leadership, Outwit and Perplex.

special_powers.name: WE SHALL BE ONE PEOPLE, AND I SHALL LEAD
special_powers.description: Flag-Smasher can use Leadership. When he does and succeeds, choose a copyable Marvel Team ability. Friendly characters with a lower point value can use that ability until your next turn.

special_powers.name: THE NATIONS OF THE WORLD SHALL CRUMBLE, AND BE ONE
special_powers.description: Opposing characters that possess or can use a team ability modify their attack and defense value by -1 unless already modified by this effect.

special_powers.name: ANTI-HEALING FACTOR
special_powers.description: Agent Zero can use Poison. If a an adjacent opposing character would be healed, instead they are dealt 1 unavoidable damage.

special_powers.name: KINETIC ABSORPTION
special_powers.description: Agent Zero can use Toughness. If Agent Zero would take more than 2 damage from a single attack, he takes 2 damage instead.

special_powers.name: KINETIC BLASTS
special_powers.description: Agent Zero can use Force Blast. When Agent Zero has no action tokens, he can use it as a free action.

special_powers.name: INFILTRATION ASSASSINATION
special_powers.description: Domino can use Running Shot and Stealth. Give Domino a free action when she has no action tokens, and until your next turn decrease her speed value by any amount and increase her range by the same amount.

special_powers.name: FATHER, UNCLE, AND ?
special_powers.description: When Siryn is adjacent to a friendly character named Banshee, Black Tom Cassidy, or Deadpool, modify Siryn's and those adjacent characters' attack values by +1 unless already modified by this effect.

special_powers.name: HYPNOTIC NOTES
special_powers.description: Siryn can use Pulse Wave. When she does and hits, choose any one hit character. After actions resolve, Siryn can use Mind Control targeting that character as a free action regardless of line of fire or force.

special_powers.name: MY OWN BRANCH OF X-FACTOR
special_powers.description: Siryn can use Leadership. When she does and succeeds, she and a character she removed an action token from can use Outwit until your next turn.

special_powers.name: I'M ALWAYS FOR HIRE
special_powers.description: Give a friendly character that possesses a copyable team ability a power action. Paladin can use that team ability until this ability is used again. When Paladin isn't on his starting click, opposing characters an be given a power action to activate this effect but, if they do, Paladin is healed of 1 damage.

special_powers.name: RESURRECTION CEREMONY
special_powers.description: Once per game when Elektra would be KO'd, you may give any number of other friendly characters with The Hand keyword an action token. If you do, place her in her starting area on click #8 and then heal her of damage equal to the number of action tokens given.

special_powers.name: THE ENVY OF ALL ASSASSINS
special_powers.description: Elektra can use Charge, Flurry and Stealth.

special_powers.name: THE MASTER OF ALL ASSASSINS
special_powers.description: Elektra can use Blades/Claws/Fangs, Incapacitate and Precision Strike.

special_powers.name: THE DEADLIEST OF ALL ASSASSINS
special_powers.description: Elektra can use Close Combat Expert, Exploit Weakness and Ranged Combat Expert.

special_powers.name: THE GUILTY MUST BE PUNISHED
special_powers.description: Once for all characters with this ability, each time an opposing character hits a friendly character, put a Guilty token on the attacker's card. When Punisher attacks a character, modify Punisher's attack value by +1 for each Guilty token on its card, and modify his damage value by +1 for every 2 tokens on its card.

special_powers.name: FRAG GRENADE
special_powers.description: Punisher can use Energy Explosion. When he does and targets only one character, damage dealt is penetrating damage.

special_powers.name: CONCENTRATED FIRE
special_powers.description: Punisher can use Ranged Combat Expert as a ranged combat action.

special_powers.name: I'LL ASSASSINATE CYCLOPS, IF YOU WON'T
special_powers.description: Red Hulk can use Running Shot, Improved Targeting: Ignores Hindering Terrain, and has a range value of 6.

special_powers.name: SOLDIER ON
special_powers.description: Red Hulk can use Running Shot, Improved Targeting: Hindering, and has a range value of 6.

special_powers.name: INFILTRATE & NEUTRALIZE
special_powers.description: Venom can use Plasticity, Running Shot, and Stealth.

special_powers.name: RUN & GRAB & WEB
special_powers.description: When Venom hits a single opposing character, roll a d6 that can't be rerolled. On a result of 4-6, that character can't make an attack during its next turn.

special_powers.name: LET THE MONSTER LOOSE
special_powers.description: When Venom attacks an opposing character, that character can use Super Senses. Once per game, give Venom a free action and when he can use this power, he can use Battle Fury and modifies all of his combat values by +2.

special_powers.name: ONLY THOSE I WANT TO CAN SEE ME
special_powers.description: Mercy can use Phasing/Teleport and Stealth.

special_powers.name: MERCY IS HELPING THE DYING ALONG THEIR PATH
special_powers.description: When an opposing character within 3 squares and line of fire would take damage, increase the damage dealt by 1 if this effect hasn't been applied to that character this turn.

special_powers.name: MERC WITH A MOUTH
special_powers.description: Give Lady Deadpool a free action and attach a Word Balloon to her, replacing any currently attached. Lady Deadpool can use the associated effects.

special_powers.name: BOTTOMLESS INTERDIMENSIONAL SATCHEL
special_powers.description: Give Lady Deadpool a free action, choose a combat symbol, and roll a d6 twice that can't be rerolled. Lady Deadpool can use the standard power indicated by the color for that combat symbol until you use this power again.

special_powers.name: INFILTRATE MY ENEMIES
special_powers.description: Before placing characters in your starting area, you may choose an opposing character that is 100 points or less not named Copycat. Copycat becomes friendly to that character's force and that character becomes friendly to your force. Any game effects assigned to each of them is now assigned to the other. When Copycat fails a roll for Shape Change, uses Regeneration, or is knocked out, after actions resolve, this effect ends and any game effects assigned to each of them is now assigned to the other.

special_powers.name: METAMORPH
special_powers.description: Copycat can use Shape Change. Give Copycat a free action and choose a standard power an adjacent friendly character or the character she exchanged with can use. Copycat can use that power until your next turn.

special_powers.name: TWO COILS
special_powers.description: When Constrictor targets two characters with a ranged combat attack, instead of dividing the damage between them, he may deal his printed damage value to both hit targets.

special_powers.name: VIBRANIUM COILS
special_powers.description: When Constrictor hits an opposing character, choose: the hit character modifies its attack value by -3 when making a ranged combat attack until your next turn, or give the hit character an action token.

special_powers.name: HIT MY HEAD FOR A BONG OF DOOM
special_powers.description: Doctor Bong can use Pulse Wave with a range value of 12. When he does, deal 1 additional damage to hit characters with 2 action tokens.

special_powers.name: DEADPOOL'S PSYCHIATRIST
special_powers.description: Doctor Bong can use Outwit and Perplex, but may only target the same character and the same combat type with both powers. Before he does and once per turn, the target character may choose a combat type and Doctor Bong can't counter powers or modify combat values of the chosen types.

special_powers.name: SIX PACK RECRUITING
special_powers.description: When you build your force, if G.W. Bridge and exactly four other characters share a keyword, you may choose one friendly character with a point value 150 points or less and that character has the shared keyword.

special_powers.name: 'NAM, A MERC, S.H.I.E.L.D. - DONE IT ALL
special_powers.description: Give G.W. Bridge a free action and choose Close Combat Expert or Ranged Combat Expert. G.W. Bridge can use the chosen power this turn.

special_powers.name: FIELD TACTICIAN
special_powers.description: G.W. Bridge can use Outwit. When he does, he may use it to target any number of characters within range and line of fire that can use the same team ability.

special_powers.name: AH, BUT I'M THE SECRET BROTHER OF THE SECRET CRUSH OF THE FIRST GRASSHOPPER!
special_powers.description: When Grasshopper is KO'd if no other friendly characters have been KO'd, after actions resolve you may place him on the map in your starting area on click #1.

special_powers.name: MAXIMUM JUMP!
special_powers.description: Give Grasshopper a double power action and remove him from the map. At the beginning of your next turn place him anywhere on the map.

special_powers.name: POWER OF THE LIVING LOA
special_powers.description: When Black Talon uses Mind Control, you may place a KO'd opposing character in an adjacent square on its starting click, and that character becomes the target. After actions resolve, that character is removed from the game.

special_powers.name: CONTROL OF THE MINDLESS UNDEAD
special_powers.description: Black Talon can use Mind Control with a range value of 8, and when he does he may target friendly characters. If all of his targets are friendly, a lower point value, and have the Monster keyword, he may use it as if had 3 bolts.

special_powers.name: SIBLING IMMUNITY
special_powers.description: Black Tome Cassidy ignores all damage dealt by characters named Banshee unless it's dealt by a close combat attack. This ability can't be ignored.

special_powers.name: PARTNERS IN CRIME
special_powers.description: If Black Tom Cassidy has no action tokens and a friendly character named Juggernaut within 3 squares would be assigned an action token, you may assign it to Black Tom Cassidy instead.

special_powers.name: AT HOME IN THE WOODS
special_powers.description: Black Tom Cassidy can use Stealth. When he occupies hindering terrain, modify his attack and defense values by +1.

special_powers.name: SHILLELAGH HEAT BLAST
special_powers.description: Black Tom Cassidy can use Force Blast. When he does, he deals half the result of the d6 roll as penetrating damage after actions resolve.

special_powers.name: MR. TOLLIVER - EMPLOYER OF VILLAINS
special_powers.description: Genesis can use Enhancement and Stealth. When an adjacent friendly character KO's an opposing character with an attack, after actions resolve, remove one action token from that friendly character and all action tokens from Genesis.

special_powers.name: YOU'LL BECOME APOCALYPSE'S GREATEST HORSEMAN!
special_powers.description: Give Genesis a free action and choose another friendly character within range and line of fire. Until your next turn, that character has the Horsemen of Apocalypse keyword and modifies all of its combat values by +1, unless already modified by this effect.

special_powers.name: ENVELOP IN DARKFORCE
special_powers.description: Shroud can use Smoke Cloud. Give Shroud a free action and place 1 hindering terrain marker in his own or an adjacent square. Remove that marker at the beginning of your next turn.

special_powers.name: BOMBARANGS
special_powers.description: Shroud can use Energy Explosion and Precision Strike.

special_powers.name: COUNTER-BLOCK
special_powers.description: Each time an opposing character targets and misses Shag-Chi with an attack, put a Counter token on this card. Give Shang-Chi a free action and remove all Counter tokens to make that many close combat attacks with a locked damage value of 2. At the end of your turn, remove all Counter tokens.

special_powers.name: THE GREATEST MARTIAL ARTIST OF OUR TIME
special_powers.description: Shang-Chi can use Close Combat Expert and Precision Strike.

special_powers.name: REPLACED IT WITH A BROKEN FORGERY
special_powers.description: When an opposing character with a relic or resource assigned to them makes an attack, that player rolls a d6 that can't be rerolled after actions resolve. On a result of 1-2, that player chooses one: remove the assigned relic from the game or remove an item attached to that resource from that game.

special_powers.name: COOLEST CAT IN THE WHOLE DARN WORLD
special_powers.description: Cat can use Charge, Flurry, and Stealth.

special_powers.name: EQUAL OF SHANG-CHI AND IRON FIST
special_powers.description: Cat can use Close Combat Expert as a close combat action.

special_powers.name: BLINK AND YOU'LL MISS ME
special_powers.description: Give Blink a power action when she has no action tokens. Place her into any square within 8 squares and make a close combat attack. If she hits you may return her to the square she occupied when the action began.

special_powers.name: GROUP TELEPORT
special_powers.description: Blink can use Flurry, Phasing/Teleport, and the Carry ability. She doesn't modify her speed value when using the Carry ability, and may carry up to 3 characters that share a keyword with her regardless of their speed combat symbols.

special_powers.name: BLINK, OR BLOCK
special_powers.description: Blink can use Combat Reflexes and Super Senses.

special_powers.name: MERC WITH A MOUTH
special_powers.description: Give Deadpool and Bob a free action and attach a Word Balloon to them, replacing any currently attached. Deadpool and Bob can use the associated effects.

special_powers.name: HIDING IS MY SUPER POWER
special_powers.description: Deadpool and Bob can use Stealth. If they are adjacent to a friendly character of 50 points or more, Deadpool and Bob can use Shape Change.

special_powers.name: RIDICULOUS REGENERATION
special_powers.description: Whenever Deadpool and Bob would be dealt damage from an attack, roll a d6 instead. On a result of 1, they take that damage plus 1. On a result of 2-3 they take the normal amount of damage. On a result of 4-5 they take 1 damage. On a result of a 6, they heal 1 damage. This power can't be countered or ignored.

special_powers.name: YOU'RE LIKE MY GOOD LUCK CHARM, BUT I DECIDED NOT TO JUST BRING YOUR FOOT
special_powers.description: Deadpool and Bob can use Probability Control, but only to target themselves or an adjacent opposing character. They can use it twice each turn.

special_powers.name: SNEAK AND KILL
special_powers.description: Wolverine and X-Men can use Sidestep and Stealth. Unhindered lines of fire drawn to Wolverine and X-23 during an opponent's turn are blocked unless Wolverine and X-23 have 2 action tokens or are adjacent to an opposing character not on its starting click.

special_powers.name: SLICE AND DICE
special_powers.description: Wolverine and X-23 can use Blades/Claws/Fangs and Flurry. When using Blades/Claws/Fangs, their minimum d6 result is 3. If they hit a character twice during a turn, they may use Incapacitate as a free action, targeting that character.

special_powers.name: DOUBLE HEALING FACTOR
special_powers.description: Give Wolverine and X-23 a free action and roll a d6. On a result of 2-5, heal Wolverine and X-23 of 1 damage. On a result of 6, heal Wolverine and X-23 of 2 damage.

special_powers.name: SIBLING IMMUNITY
special_powers.description: Banshee ignores all damage dealt by characters named Black Tom Cassidy unless it's dealt by a close combat attack. This ability can't be ignored.

special_powers.name: IT'S GOING TO GET A LITTLE LOUD
special_powers.description: Opposing characters within 6 squares can't use Super Senses. Opposing characters within 6 squares can't use Impervious, Invincible, or Invulnerability but can use Toughness instead. When Banshee hits a character that can't use a power due to this trait, increase damage dealt to that character by 1.

special_powers.name: SONIC SCREAM
special_powers.description: Banshee can use Pulse Wave. When he does, if you give him a double power action instead he can use Improved Targeting: Destroy Blocking.

special_powers.name: BODYSLIDE
special_powers.description: Cable can use Running Shot and Improved Movement: Elevated, Hindering, Blocking.

special_powers.name: TECHNOPATH
special_powers.description: Opposing characters within Cable's range and line of fire modify their attack value by -2 when making a ranged combat attack.

special_powers.name: TELEPATHIC FUTURE LEADER
special_powers.description: Cable can use Leadership, Outwit, and Probability Control. This power can't be countered.

special_powers.name: AVX #T002 X-MEN
special_powers.description: This team character can use Leadership, Phasing/Teleport, and Sidestep.

special_powers.name: SPEED CYCLONE UPLIFT
special_powers.description: When Speed Demon moves, after actions resolve, choose an opposing character and roll a d6. If the result is less than the number of distinct squares that Speed Demon moved into or through that are adjacent to that character during the move, you may place that character within line of fire of its square and up to the result away in squares and deal that character half of the result in damage.

special_powers.name: TWO-FER
special_powers.description: Speed Demon can use Hypersonic Speed. When he does, during his move, he may be given a free action to make a second close combat attack.

special_powers.name: WELLSPRING OF POWER
special_powers.description: Speed Demon can use Perplex. He can modify a combat value other than damage by +2 when targeting himself or a character that shares a keyword with him.

special_powers.name: THE WORLD AT 500 MPH
special_powers.description: Whizzer can use Hypersonic Speed. When he does, during his move, he may be given a free action to make a second close combat attack.

special_powers.name: FRICTION SHIELD
special_powers.description: Whizzer can use Combat Reflexes and Super Senses.

special_powers.name: BODY BLUR
special_powers.description: Whizzer can use Stealth, if he used Hypersonic Speed during your last turn.

special_powers.name: YOU CLONED WHO?!?
special_powers.description: Give Arnim Zola a free action to place a Gwen Stacy Clone bystander token as described on this card adjacent to him on the map. If there is already 1 friendly one on the map, this is a power action instead. If there are 2 or more friendly ones, this is a double power action instead.

special_powers.name: CLONE MASTER
